plmxml_bus:QueryClause.stringValue: SELECT qid FROM GET6ECNRevision WHERE "items_tag.item_id" = "${ECN ID = }" AND "active_seq" = "1" AND "items_tag.object_name" = "${Name = }" AND "owning_user.user_id" = "${Owning User = }" AND "owning_organization.name" = "${Owning Group = }" AND "fnd0InProcess" = "${Is Submitted? = }" AND "release_status_list.name" = "${Status = }" AND "creation_date" >= "${CreatedAfter = }" AND "creation_date" <= "${CreatedBefore = }" AND "date_released" >= "${ReleasedAfter = }" AND "date_released" <= "${ReleasedBefore = }" AND "GET6EngrApproval:HasParticipant.GroupMember:assignee.User:user.user_id" = "${Engr Approval = }" AND "GET6OptionalReviewer:HasParticipant.GroupMember:assignee.User:user.user_id" = "${Optional Reviewer = }" AND "GET6Producibility:HasParticipant.GroupMember:assignee.User:user.user_id" = "${Producibility = }" AND "CMClosure" = "${ECN Closure = }" AND "CMDisposition" = "${ECN Disposition = }" AND "CMMaturity" = "${ECN Maturity = }" AND "get6EngrProdLine" = "${get6EngrProdLine = }" AND "get6Customers" = "${get6Customers = }" AND "get6OrderNo" = "${get6OrderNo = }" AND "get6WtImpactNo" = "${get6WtImpactNo = }" AND "get6ReasonCode" = "${get6ReasonCode = }" AND "get6ChangeReason" = "${get6ChangeReason = }" AND "get6PartsCatalogs" = "${get6PartsCatalogs = }" AND "get6PatToolsNC" = "${get6PatToolsNC = }" AND "get6IsMatlAtMfgLocn" = "${get6IsMatlAtMfgLocn = }" AND "get6IsMatlAtServiceLocn" = "${get6IsMatlAtServiceLocn = }" AND "get6BypassCheckmate" = "${get6BypassCheckmate = }" AND "get6BypassComments" = "${get6BypassComments = }" AND "get6BypassReason" = "${get6BypassReason = }" AND "get6ModDesignCutIn" = "${get6ModDesignCutIn = }" AND "get6CASECNNumber" = "${get6CASECNNumber = }" AND "get6PlannerCode" = "${get6PlannerCode = }" ORDER BY items_tag.item_id ASCENDING USERENTRY item_id
